      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lime</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl, then season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
