    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>zingy salad</strong> topped with the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>coriander leaves </strong>– this is your <strong>Indian-style chicken salad with spicy green chutney</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>nigella seeds</strong> over the top</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
